Interface IAtomList

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AtomArrayList, AtomListWrapper, AtomPair, AtomsetArray, AtomSetSinglet

    public interface IAtomList
    Interface for a set of IAtoms. The IAtomSet might contain 0, 1, 2 or many IAtoms.
